properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const w = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower Group').content('Arm').content('Arm Fill').content('Arm End').size[0];const l = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}').effect('Limber System')('ikfkfreeksides')[1];const splt = thisLayer.effect('The Kasra')('Split') * 0.01;createPath([	[w*0.5, -l],	[w*0.5, -l * splt],	[-w*0.5, -l * splt],	[-w*0.5, -l],], [], [], true)

properties.name: Size
properties.expression: const w = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke 1').strokeWidth + thisLayer.effect('The Kasra')('Outline Width') * (thisLayer.effect('The Kasra')('Auto-scale') == 0 ? 1 : thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0]);[w, w * thisLayer.effect('The Kasra')('Rounding') * 0.01]

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const w = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke 1').strokeWidth + thisLayer.effect('The Kasra')('Outline Width') * (thisLayer.effect('The Kasra')('Auto-scale') == 0 ? 1 : thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0]);const l = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}').effect('Limber System')('ikfkfreeksides')[1] * thisLayer.effect('The Kasra')('Split') * 0.01;const verts = [	[w*0.5, 0],	[w*0.5, -l],	[-w*0.5, -l],	[-w*0.5, 0],]createPath(verts, [], [], false)

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function upperStrokePath() {        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('curvature').value[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('inTangPos').value;            const outTangPos = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('outTangPos').value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos], [[0, 0], thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1)], false);        }    }upperStrokePath();

properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke 1').strokeWidth + effect('The Kasra')('Outline Width') * 2 * (thisLayer.effect('The Kasra')('Auto-scale') == 0 ? 1 : thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0])

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('scaleFactor').value[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;[scaleFactor * widthScale, 0]
